this test suite problem needs ENABLE_AMESOS build for the parallel run, and a standard build for the serial run. 

the two runs/tests that should be made:

mpirun -np 2 -machinefile machinefile goma_exe -se stderr -so stdout -a -i input_axi_restart

here the diffs should be of stderr and stdout with stderr1 and stdout1
This run must have amesos build
this run takes just under 6 min to complete
